Package net.tangly.core.crm

Class NaturalEntity

java.lang.Object
net.tangly.core.EntityExtendedImp
net.tangly.core.crm.NaturalEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
CrmEntity, Entity, EntityExtended, HasComments, HasDateRange, HasId, HasLocation, HasName, HasOid, HasTags, HasText
public class NaturalEntity extends EntityExtendedImp implements EntityExtended, CrmEntity
A natural entity is a person. A natural entity has an identity defined as the legal number of a person (e.g., the social security number, a name defined as the last name and the first name separated by a comma, a life duration and a text describing it.

A potential approach for a natural person identification is ISO 24366.
